License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This package offers easy integration with http://webfonts.biz
        
        After installing it you need to setup your apikey using
        the control panel configlet at portal_url/@@webfonts-settings
        
        Having done so, you need to specify the DOM elements you want
        to replace, and what font to use by customizing
        skins/webfonts/webfonts.js.
        
        
        
        
